01:26:41.750 --> 01:26:43.740
or four times resting.

01:26:43.740 --> 01:26:44.573
- Okay, but it seems like-

01:26:44.573 --> 01:26:48.170
- Whereas exercise can
take you up 10 times.

01:26:48.170 --> 01:26:49.003
- Got it. All right.

