01:38:55.780 --> 01:38:57.500
and your heat production.

01:38:57.500 --> 01:39:02.500
And the really extreme example
is hyper and hypothyroidism.

01:39:02.850 --> 01:39:05.730
People that are hyperthyroid or fidgety

01:39:05.730 --> 01:39:07.680
and they have a high metabolic rate

01:39:07.680 --> 01:39:09.420
and they're hot.

01:39:09.420 --> 01:39:12.283
And people that are hypothermic are cool.

01:39:13.510 --> 01:39:15.250
They don't move very much.

01:39:15.250 --> 01:39:17.850
So any kind of muscle activity increases,

01:39:17.850 --> 01:39:20.580
and when you say it's not much activity,

01:39:20.580 --> 01:39:23.480
but remember it's only 20% effective.

01:39:23.480 --> 01:39:26.943
80% of the energy is going to heat.

01:39:27.800 --> 01:39:32.280
So it may not exert much energy
to tap your foot. [chuckles]

01:39:32.280 --> 01:39:36.320
But four times the amount
of energy that is going

01:39:36.320 --> 01:39:39.400
into the movement is being lost as heat.

01:39:39.400 --> 01:39:41.900
- That's very interesting.

